title#:#Resets failed login attempts and reactivates corresponding users
description#:#This plugin allows to implement a soft lockout by resetting failed login attempts and reactivating corresponding users after a while.
lockout_duration#:#Duration of Lockout
lockout_duration_desc#:#The actual duration of the lockout varies depending on the settings of the lockout duration and the schedule of this cron job. To avoid locking somebody out for longer than the indicated time, all users deactivated more than lockout_duration - cron_schedule will be reactivated.